replies.body:
Honestly even CertainlyT making unique/fun champions is 100% arguable. If CertainlyT can't make a balanced and healthy champion without overloading their kits absolutely then that would be awesome, but he like most designers are constantly producing toxic champions who have severe balance issues. I think in general the entire champion design team needs to be totally changed and issues with all of the recent champions need to be dealt with like nearly every release coming with at least one  - infinite dashes or a boring and somewhat toxic 3-hit-2-win feature that nobody likes. It's not just CertainlyT producing trash designs.

